# Configure AI Collaborators

<!--Add me to TOCs-->

<!--Add mentions to other AI Articles-->

{{highlighted-preview-article-level}}

AI Collaborators are a way to onboard AI agents into your projects and tasks. You can configure an AI Collaborator with brand guidelines, then assign it to a task as you would a user.

Currently, AI Collaborators can be used to review content. More AI Collaborator capabilities will be available in the future.


